{"tid":221383,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急) BB貓食咩糧好？","createTime":"2017-04-28T16:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T17:41:50.000Z","uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0eee97ca1d78fdafbbeea0188fab61f9129f51c9","tid":221383,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:11:36.000Z","msg":"我領養左兩隻貓bb 星期日接返黎啦<br />\n我已經準備好貓砂 盤 玩具 籠 濕糧<br />\n總之準備左好多野...<br />\n唯一我唔知買咩乾糧好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問左好多養貓嘅朋友<br />\n 一開始話Rc隻幼貓糧<br />\n但係另一個朋友話多味精叫我買nutrience<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係行左幾次旺角都搵唔到 <br />\n而家好擔心<br />\n其實我應該係跟返原本佢屋企食既糧再慢慢溝<br />\n定係我可以用濕糧溝新乾糧 俾佢試下習慣下？<br />\n屌 好迷惘 求救 <br />\n話我知點好 話我知咩bb糧又天然又容易買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00fcab1c3a87d88ac38ed4cd3e0c4a00e05197d","tid":221383,"uid":10268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"我前排係灣仔見到有 <br />\n你可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f9e6139912d7aae6c61da8bfe0a9b13b05053a","tid":221383,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我前排係灣仔見到有 <br />\n你可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真？不過好遠 我唔想我老公去咁遠買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8016c8e46c88871fbdd767ff06c5f8dd386f8244","tid":221383,"uid":10268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我前排係灣仔見到有 <br />\n你可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><