3518e4d14c2","tid":221383,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Origen cat &amp;kitten 配方 <br />\n每餐再溝少少雞肉落去一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪容易買到架？"},{"pid":"e0e36b79acd51c6aa3b6817d6a20ff570a643f39","tid":221383,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:35:15.000Z","msg":"係咪有經濟考慮急住食乾糧？<br />\n得2個月由濕食罐頭開始先，揀單一蛋白來源(得一種肉成分)嘅主食罐，好似canagan同thrive, 食落無咩問題可以揀埋nature's variety instinct 雞罐，多少少脂肪<br />\n<br />\n到3,4個月再漫漫減少濕糧，加翻少少乾糧，由幾粒開始<br />\n<br />\n濕糧成分無乾糧咁複雜，無咁易令貓屙，尤其純雞罐，類似自己蒸雞柳咁，但就加左唔同營養素，會好好多<br />\n幼貓唔好長期喺正餐食自制食物，除非有加營養素(牛磺酸、omega 3同6、鈣粉、維他命嗰啲)，如果唔係身體會較差<br />\n<br />\n不過都建議每日有一次濕食補水，幼貓自細比佢飲多啲水養成習慣，生結石同慢性腎病嗰啲9成都係餵乾糧<br />\n<br />\n有關貓糧條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我諗包括哂大部分喺香港買到嘅乾糧濕糧生肉糧，當然都keep住update<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I254f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3a572897\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak</a>"},{"pid":"b01f1518ab9d3cb5380d684929e9aaae29dd1245","tid":221383,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有經濟考慮急住食乾糧？<br />\n得2個月由濕食罐頭開始先，揀單一蛋白來源(得一種肉成分)嘅主食罐，好似canagan同thrive, 食落無咩問題可以揀埋nature's variety instinct 雞罐，多少少脂肪<br />\n<br />\n到3,4個月再漫漫減少濕糧，加翻少少乾糧，由幾粒開始<br />\n<br />\n濕糧成分無乾糧咁複雜，無咁易令貓屙，尤其純雞罐，類似自己蒸雞柳咁，但就加左唔同營養素，會好好多<br />\n幼貓唔好長期喺正餐食自制食物，除非有加營養素(牛磺酸、omega 3同6、鈣粉、維他命嗰啲)，如果唔係身體會較差<br />\n<br />\n不過都建議每日有一次濕食補水，幼貓自細比佢飲多啲水養成習慣，生結石同慢性腎病嗰啲9成都係餵乾糧<br />\n<br />\n有關貓糧條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我諗包括哂大部分喺香港買到嘅乾糧濕糧生肉糧，當然都keep住update<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I254f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3a572897\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak</a></blockquote><br />\n其實冇架 我已經買定一大盒濕糧俾佢<br />\n不過係我朋友叫我溝下少少乾糧 等佢習慣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b28776d79c268564c015a8c6b88eac3d4e119a8","tid":221383,"uid":30568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:58:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"869a65a7c61d67d59c3bdec2e1fad1e87d714936","tid":221383,"uid":66669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果隻食緊wellness core kitten formula</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果隻食到由排骨精變到精實肌肉<br />\n當初都係睇個乾糧資料庫揀<br />\n加埋濕糧"}]}